    "Ensuring patient confidentiality while allowing for largescale data analysis requires robust safeguards, such as encryption and decentralized data-sharing models [46].",
    "Federated learning, which enables AI models to learn from data stored locally without transferring it, offers a promising solution by preserving privacy while maintaining diagnostic accuracy.",
    "By building trust through secure data-handling practices, healthcare systems can foster greater acceptance of AI among both clinicians and patients.To establish trust and reliability, AI technologies require rigorous validation before widespread deployment.",
